org.forgerock.openam.ldap

Class LdapFromJsonQueryFilterVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.ldap.LdapFromJsonQueryFilterVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.forgerock.util.query.QueryFilterVisitor<org.forgerock.opendj.ldap.Filter,Void,org.forgerock.json.JsonPointer>

    public class LdapFromJsonQueryFilterVisitor
extends Object
implements org.forgerock.util.query.QueryFilterVisitor<org.forgerock.opendj.ldap.Filter,Void,org.forgerock.json.JsonPointer>
    This class is primarily intended to convert Json (from an incoming query filter) into an LDAP compatible query. This is based on James's LdapQueryFilterVisitor.
